1. Press 'Load' Button to open camera.
2. Press any slide bar to complete opening camera (this's a bug for this program.)
3. slide bar to calibrate HSV
4. Edit text box beside slide bar is range of error.
5. Press 'read file' to read all value in file.
6. Press 'write file' to write all value into file.

about file :
  first line is range of error value.
  second line is HSV calibrated value.
